<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-label">The Process</div>
  <h1>Simple. Specific. <em>Guaranteed.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-sub">One structured interview. A written report within one week showing every automation opportunity with real numbers. Yours to keep no matter what you decide after.</p>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-label">Four Phases</div>
  <h2>Assess. Report. Optimize. <em>Automate.</em></h2>
  <p>Every Kodiak engagement follows the same proven sequence. We never build before we understand. We never automate before we optimize.</p>

  <div class="phases">
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-num"><div class="phase-n">1</div><div class="phase-tag">Assess</div></div>
      <div class="phase-content">
        <div class="phase-title">A fully comprehensive interview — in person or remote</div>
        <p class="phase-desc">We take the time to fully understand every aspect of your business and how it operates. The more we know about your processes, your team, and where friction exists, the more accurate and valuable your report will be. No detail is too small — the quality of your assessment depends entirely on how well we understand your operation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-num"><div class="phase-n">2</div><div class="phase-tag">Report</div></div>
      <div class="phase-content">
        <div class="phase-title">Written report delivered within one week</div>
        <p class="phase-desc">Your $1,000 assessment delivers a written report including 3-4 automations or business flow optimizations ready to implement — each one showing exactly how much time and money it recovers. Plus a long-term plan showing every other opportunity we identified during your interview. The report is yours to keep regardless of what you decide after.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-num"><div class="phase-n">3</div><div class="phase-tag">Optimize</div></div>
      <div class="phase-content">
        <div class="phase-title">Simplify before you automate</div>
        <p class="phase-desc">Before we build anything we map your current processes and eliminate waste. A 15-step process simplified to 7 and then automated delivers three times the value of speeding up a broken workflow. Most consultants skip this step. We never do.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-num"><div class="phase-n">4</div><div class="phase-tag">Automate</div></div>
      <div class="phase-content">
        <div class="phase-title">We build it, train your team, and manage it</div>
        <p class="phase-desc">For clients ready to move forward — we configure every tool, connect every integration, train every team member, and manage it ongoing. You focus on the work that needs a person. Everything else runs itself.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="guarantee-box">
    <p><strong>The Guarantee:</strong> Every assessment identifies 3-4 actionable solutions you can implement yourself — each one guaranteed to save measurable time and money. We guarantee at least 5 hours returned per week and $1,000 in monthly recoverable value or your fee is fully refunded.</p>
  </div>
</section>

